900
00:40:14,539 --> 00:40:16,099
So maybe...

901
00:40:16,099 --> 00:40:16,659
Yan Fei.

902
00:40:20,260 --> 00:40:21,340
Are you out of your mind?

903
00:40:22,380 --> 00:40:23,420
Dad told me

904
