915
00:40:44,820 --> 00:40:45,860
I'm just the messenger.

916
00:40:46,380 --> 00:40:47,740
I even paid for lunch.

917
00:40:48,059 --> 00:40:48,980
What did I do wrong?

918
00:40:50,099 --> 00:40:51,900
You broke up
with the British guy years ago.

919
00:40:51,900 --> 00:40:52,619
Why still single?

920
00:40:53,659 --> 00:40:54,900
But I'm still young.

921
00:40:54,900 --> 00:40:56,300
